2002-04-10 Jim Garlick <garlick@llnl.gov>

	* quota.c : Add -f option to read config file from user-specified path.

	* quota.c : Tru64 users in more than sixteen 
	groups would fail authunix_create_default().  
	Call authunix_create() instead [Dave Fox, GNATS #48].

